column5: I found a new lake that I was thinking of giving a try, I only drove by it so I really know nothing about it Tallan Lake South of Bancroft.  Anyone know anything about it
According to the MNR Fish-Online web app it has Lake Trout, Pumpkinseed, Smallmouth and Perch in it.   However, based on feedback on the boards, I am not sure how accurate Fish-Online is.
